Title: IOU
Text:
It is hereby acknowledged that Fuze borrowed 10 thousand Credits from Kuixiao as the former wishes to replace his Terminal. It is agreed that the debt should be repayed before 2502, March 11th with interests in one installment. The interest rate is agreed to be 7% per month. In witness whereof, we sign this document.

Borrower: Fuze
Witness: Bo
